PARS Paper wallet

Offline ParsiCoin paper wallet generator

This page generates a new ParsiCoin paperwallet with mnemonic seed. It is self contained 100% JavaScript that works in your browser and does all the necessary calculations locally, so you can save this page and generate a new wallet on a machine that is not connected to the network. Secret key to your wallet is generated in your browser and never sent to our servers. This way, you can create a ParsiCoin wallet without risking the keys.
